<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.6">
<l>caṅkaraṉait tāḻnta caṭaiyāṉai yaccaṭaimēṟ</l>
<l>poṅkaravam vaittukanta puṇṇiyaṉai yaṅkorunā</l>
<l>ḷāvāveṉ ṟāḻāmaik kāppāṉai yeppoḻutu</l>
<l>mōvātu neñcē yurai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Śaṅkara, he with the hanging matted locks, the meritorious one</l>
<l>who rejoices in putting squirming snakes in those matted locks, the one who</l>
<l>will protect [us] one day there from sinking pitifully, always</l>
<l>without stopping speak of him, heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
